rom\": 3238, \"to\": 3252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it had to go to a photo finish to decide it...Five one-thousandths of a second the difference between gold and silver, and the gold is going to the United States.\\\"\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3424, \"end\": 3437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970698952165, \"rank\": 2.9172217855009733e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photo finish\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"Five one-thousandths\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3369}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on Lyles: \\\"You have got to give this guy credit.\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"this guy credit\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the talk this year, all the posturing\\u2026He has silenced every single critic.\\\"\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every single critic\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on the leadup to the men's 100m: \\\"You could run 100 100m dashes in your life, none of them are going to feel like the pressure and the anticipation and the excitement that you are feeling right now.\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the leadup\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3598}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100m\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3616}, {\"ngram\"